<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="id522d6294-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Historical and Revision Notes</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Based on title 28, U.S.C., 1940 ed., § 175 (<ref href="/us/act/1911-03-03/ch231/s95">Mar. 3, 1911, ch. 231, § 95</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/36/1119">36 Stat. 1119</ref>; <ref href="/us/act/1912-08-23/ch344">Aug. 23, 1912, ch. 344</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/37/357">37 Stat. 357</ref>; <ref href="/us/act/1926-02-20/ch23">Feb. 20, 1926, ch. 23</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/44/8">44 Stat. 8</ref>).</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Changes in arrangement and phraseology were made.</p>
</note>
